item.dc:creator: @ry60003333 ry60003333
item.description:
@ry60003333 wrote:

Any server you find here is not going to hold more then 35+ people. Believe me, I learned that a long time ago. Try Dodian’s Uber Server or write your own server from scratch. Personally I’m making my own from scratch, and it is amazing how fast a clean well written server runs.

But again since you probably can’t do that, look for Dodian’s “source”.
